{"tid":2450532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢控主任黃華芬被停職　曾向鄭若驊發信轟警方公然說謊損司法制度","createTime":"2021-03-17T12:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T13:34:08.000Z","uid":261647,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90b0e5ee225cbf8ebb28615230312c7affab9481","tid":2450532,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/星島-檢控主任黃華芬被停職-曾向鄭若驊發信轟警方公然說謊損司法制度/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E9%BB%83%E8%8F%AF%E8%8A%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7-%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1%E8%BD%9F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E7%84%B6%E8%AA%AA%E8%AC%8A%E6%90%8D%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=6cd21685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E9%BB%83%E8%8F%AF%E8%8A%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%81%B7-%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%91%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1%E8%BD%9F%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E7%84%B6%E8%AA%AA%E8%AC%8A%E6%90%8D%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%2F&h=b053e938\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/星島-檢控主任黃華芬被停職-曾向鄭若驊發信轟警方公然說謊損司法制度/</a><br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》今（ 17 日）引消息指，東區裁判法院高級二等檢控主任黃華芬早前已被停職接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n黃華芬於前年反修例運動期間、2019 年 9 月，以當時「法庭檢控主任會」主席名義，發出題為「警方公然說謊，損害司法制度」的電郵，向律政司司長鄭若驊及時任刑事檢控專員梁卓然投訴。信中指出，831 是一個敏感日子，但警方在 831 前拘捕鄭松泰，黃之鋒及區諾軒等 7 人，並於同日的記者會上，公開否認拘捕行動與 831 有關。"},{"pid":"585b25a8643ad812dd6eb02cefa32a11b276cd6f","tid":2450532,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1590b9ed